<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Прайс-лист — ООО «Компания Кофе и Чая»</title>
<style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f5f5f7;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --ink: #1d1d1f;
      --ink-secondary: #6e6e73;
      --ink-tertiary: #86868b;
      --line: #e5e5ea;
      --line-light: #f0f0f2;
      --accent: #0071e3;
      --accent-light: #e8f2fd;
      --green: #30a158;
      --green-bg: #e9f7ef;
      --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
      --shadow-md: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      --shadow-lg: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      --radius-sm: 12px;
      --radius-md: 18px;
      --radius-lg: 24px;
      --radius-pill: 980px;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Display', 'SF Pro Text', 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.47059;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .doc { max-width: 1120px; margin: 40px auto 60px; }

    /* ---- Hero ---- */
    .hero {
      padding: 56px 48px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      background: transparent;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      padding: 6px 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 56px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .hero .lead {
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 620px;
      font-size: 19px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--ink-secondary);
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    /* ---- Nav ---- */
    .nav-wrap {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      padding: 0 48px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(180%);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px) saturate(180%);
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      padding: 8px 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.04), 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    }
    .nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      padding: 9px 18px;
      transition: all 0.15s ease;
    }
    .nav a:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* ---- Summary ---- */
    .summary {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ sections|length }}, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 0 48px 8px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    {% if sections|length > 5 %}
    @media (min-width: 801px) { .summary { grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); } }
    {% endif %}
    .summary-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: 18px 20px 16px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }
    .summary-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
    .summary-card .icon { font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1; }
    .summary-card strong {
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: var(--ink);
      display: block;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    .summary-card span {
      color: var(--ink-tertiary);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 4px;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ---- Section ---- */
    .section { padding: 0 48px 32px; page-break-before: always; }
    .section:first-of-type { page-break-before: auto; }
    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .section-icon {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: var(--card);
      font-size: 22px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .section h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    /* ---- Brand Card ---- */
    .brand-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      page-break-inside: avoid;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }
    .brand-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); }
    .brand-card-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 22px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-light);
    }
    .brand-card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .brand-card-head p {
      margin: 5px 0 0;
      color: var(--ink-tertiary);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .count {
      min-width: 56px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      background: #f2f2f5;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .count span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 4px;
      text-transform: lowercase;
      color: var(--ink-tertiary);
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    /* ---- Table ---- */
    .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; }
    th {
      background: #f5f5f7;
      color: var(--ink-secondary);
      text-align: left;
      padding: 11px 14px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    th:not(:first-child) { text-align: center; }
    td {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-light);
      vertical-align: top;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    td:not(:first-child) { text-align: center; }
    tbody tr:nth-child(even) td { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.012); }
    tbody tr:hover td { background: #f0f4ff; }
    .price-table td:last-child,
    .price-table td:nth-last-child(2) {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--green);
      white-space: nowrap;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }
    .price-table th:last-child,
    .price-table th:nth-last-child(2) { text-align: center; }

    .name-col { text-align: left !important; }

    /* ---- Footer ---- */
    .footer {
      padding: 28px 48px 32px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--ink-tertiary);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer strong { color: var(--ink-secondary); font-weight: 600; }

    /* ---- Print ---- */
    @page { size: A4; margin: 11mm; }
    @media print {
      body { background: #fff; color: #000; }
      .doc { box-shadow: none; margin: 0; max-width: none; }
      .nav-wrap { display: none; }
      .hero { padding: 12mm 0 8mm; text-align: left; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 24px; }
      .hero .lead { font-size: 11px; }
      .hero-badge { display: none; }
      .summary { grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); padding: 4mm 0 0; gap: 4px; }
      .summary-card { box-shadow: none; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px 10px; }
      .summary-card strong { font-size: 20px; }
      .section { padding: 6mm 0 0; }
      .section h2 { font-size: 18px; }
      .section-icon { box-shadow: none; }
      .brand-card { box-shadow: none; border: 1px solid #ddd; break-inside: avoid; page-break-inside: avoid; margin-bottom: 12px; }
      .brand-card-head { padding: 10px 12px; }
      .brand-card h3 { font-size: 15px; }
      table { font-size: 9px; }
      th { font-size: 7.5px; padding: 5px 6px; }
      td { padding: 5px 6px; font-size: 9px; }
      .count { font-size: 15px; padding: 6px 8px; }
      .footer { border-top: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 8mm 0; }
      .nav { display: none; }
    }

    /* ---- Mobile ---- */
    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .doc { margin: 16px 0; }
      .hero, .nav-wrap, .section, .summary, .footer { padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; }
      .hero { padding-top: 36px; padding-bottom: 28px; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 36px; }
      .hero .lead { font-size: 16px; }
      .summary { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 10px; }
      .brand-card-head { flex-direction: column; }
      .section h2 { font-size: 26px; }
      .nav { border-radius: 24px; }
    }

    th { text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; }
    th.name-col { text-align: left; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="doc">

<header class="hero">
<div class="hero-badge">ООО «Компания Кофе и Чая»</div>
<h1>Прайс-лист</h1>
<p class="lead">Ассортимент для HoReCa, офисов, ресторанов, отелей и корпоративных клиентов: кофе, чай, молоко и альтернатива, сиропы и кордиалы, вода и напитки.</p>
</header>

<div class="nav-wrap">
<nav class="nav">
{% for s in sections %}
<a href="#{{ s.id }}">{{ s.icon }} {{ s.title_ru }}</a>
{% endfor %}
</nav>
</div>

<section class="summary">
{% for s in sections %}
{% set count = counts.get(s.id, 0) %}
<div class="summary-card">
<div class="icon">{{ s.icon }}</div>
<strong>{{ count }}</strong>
<span>{{ s.title_ru }}</span>
</div>
{% endfor %}
</section>

{% for s in sections %}
<section class="section" id="{{ s.id }}">
<div class="section-head">
<div class="section-icon">{{ s.icon }}</div>
<h2>{{ s.title_ru }}</h2>
</div>

{% for b in brands if b.section_id == s.id %}
{% set prods = products_by_brand.get(b.id, []) %}
<article class="brand-card">
<div class="brand-card-head">
<div>
<h3>{{ b.title_ru }}</h3>
{% if b.subtitle_ru %}
<p>{{ b.subtitle_ru }}</p>
{% endif %}
</div>
<div class="count">{{ prods|length }}<span>поз.</span></div>
</div>
<div class="table-wrap">
<table class="price-table">
<thead><tr>
<th class="name-col">НАИМЕНОВАНИЕ</th>
{% for key in b.attr_keys %}
<th>{{ key }}</th>
{% endfor %}
{% for pi in b.price_col_indices %}
{% set h = b.column_headers[pi] %}
<th>{{ h }}</th>
{% endfor %}
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
{% for p in prods %}
<tr>
<td>{{ p.name_ru }}</td>
{% for key in b.attr_keys %}
<td>{{ p.attrs.get(key, '') }}</td>
{% endfor %}
<td>{{ p.price_1_fmt }}</td>
{% if b.has_dual_pricing and b.price_col_indices|length >= 2 %}
<td>{{ p.price_2_fmt }}</td>
{% endif %}
</tr>
{% endfor %}
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</article>
{% endfor %}
</section>
{% endfor %}
</div>

<footer class="footer">
<strong>ООО «Компания Кофе и Чая»</strong> / Don't Worry Group &nbsp;·&nbsp; Прайс-лист &nbsp;·&nbsp; Актуально на дату экспорта
</footer>

</body>
</html>
